{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1a52538841","title":"在宣传中不说打台湾西藏的时间","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3c397f92e","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":29,"articleId":"1a52538841"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"668999b34c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东写给中共中央宣传部副部长、中央人民政府新闻总署署长胡乔木的信。"}],"contents":[{"id":"545f03c9da","type":"title","text":"在宣传中不说打台湾西藏的时间！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841"},{"id":"668999b34c","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841"},{"id":"4cab6a496e","type":"paragraph","text":"请查过去宣传中有无规定在一九五〇年打台湾的事，有人说他看过今年元旦文件内说今年要打台湾的话，未知确否？以后请注意，只说要打台湾西藏，不说任何时间。各党派贺词中一九五一年任务我已全部删去，因其中有打台湾西藏一项","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841"},{"id":"ef60764272","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841"},{"id":"339dea95ca","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841"}],"page":{"id":"7dd487f198","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"1a52538841","start":194,"end":194}}}},"__N_SSG":true}